.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
PyMailq (sel:608)> select size \-5000
PyMailq (sel:437)> select sender MAILER\-DAEMON
PyMailq (sel:316)> select status active
PyMailq (sel:0)>
